{"tid":371790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門風災增至８人死亡　料死亡人數持續上升","createTime":"2017-08-24T01:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T03:07:17.000Z","uid":58099,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79e8dac8342672675b5827f5c6c65d455c7ba753","tid":371790,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:46:39.000Z","msg":"颱風「天鴿」橫掃澳門，帶來狂風暴雨，多個地下停車場水浸。民防中心表示，消防員凌晨三時許及四時許，先後在沙梨頭典雅灣停車場，發現兩具屍體，風暴令超過３００人受傷，死亡人數增至８人，料死亡人數持續上升。<br />\n<br />\n同樣發生水浸的灝景峰、恆德大廈及青怡大廈等三個地下停車場，消防仍在場進行排水及搜救工作。截至清晨，澳門共發生三百四十三宗事故報告，包括建築物損毀、石屎脫落、招牌廣告簷篷搖搖欲墜等。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官崔世安向死者表示哀悼，會盡力幫助傷者，指天鴿造成的影響非常嚴重，承諾會盡全力做好這次救災工作。"},{"pid":"e094065308a68fee56217ccd1cffe08464eb08e7","tid":371790,"uid":120537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:49:07.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"be2e6c4facc48b5bba9a9de9b7db9299cfcb4821","tid":371790,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"睇黎尋晚話個fd做消防死左幾十個人單野係堅"},{"pid":"9e716502f1665c1b8178dda094f0777188140ad4","tid":371790,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"幾乎全浸實唔止八個"},{"pid":"3e8f81686739774e42256fdeafe0f0e4fbd6ff11","tid":371790,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:56:27.000Z","msg":"咁撚遲先掛9號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113145b93c548d1bb173d5d9239211755bc693dc","tid":371790,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239290e27591b7a9129f0c5731be2516620bad8a","tid":371790,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T02:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img